art's top podcasts\", \"from\": 6740, \"to\": 6761}, {\"ngram\": \"tune-in\", \"from\": 6775, \"to\": 6782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The play-by-play channels will enable iHeart's listeners to hear NBCU's coverage of the most exciting moments of the Games, with a special focus on Team USA.\", \"from\": 6819, \"to\": 6976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6884, \"end\": 6888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCU\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 6967, \"end\": 6975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997477755739839, \"rank\": 0.0002522755083673205, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"play\", \"from\": 6831, \"to\": 6835}, {\"ngram\": \"iHeart's listeners\", \"from\": 6857, \"to\": 6875}, {\"ngram\": \"the most exciting moments\", \"from\": 6903, \"to\": 6928}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 6932, \"to\": 6941}, {\"ngram\": \"a special focus\", \"from\": 6948, \"to\": 6963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The U.S. has led the medal count at seven consecutive Summer Games and looks to be a powerhouse again.\", \"from\": 6977, \"to\": 7079, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The U.S.\", \"from\": 6977, \"to\": 6985}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal count\", \"from\": 6994, \"to\": 7009}, {\"ngram\": \"seven consecutive Summer Games\", \"from\": 7013, \"to\": 7043}, {\"ngram\": \"a powerhouse\", \"from\": 7060, \"to\": 7072}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBCU's coverage on iHeart's channels is expected to include Team USA men's and women's basketball, soccer, and volleyball, as well as swimming, gymnastics, track & field, and more.\", \"from\": 7080, \"to\": 7260, \"entities